Third Department,

March, 1954.

(March 24, 1954.) In the Matter of the Estate of Louis B. Basten, Deceased. Myrtle J. Basten, Appellant; Austin S. Basten, as Executor of Louis D. Basten, Deceased, Respondent.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, by default, without costs. Foster, P. J., Bergan, Coon and Imrie, JJ., concur. [204 Misc. 937.]
